year4_current_source: The reference cited was from the start of the year and stated the plan. My estimate is based on aluminum production (143,800) consuming 287,600 tons of alumina. Trade data shows 21,200 tons was exported from the US to Venezuela (See table 3 Bauxite MIS Q4 2018.) Jamaica Bauxite Institute data shows 31,500 tons exported to Venezuela. Subtracting the imports leaves about 240,000 needed to produce the amount of aluminum reported.
